    <div class="col-lg-6">
      <h4>Rating based on reviews</h4>
      <p>Rating is regard to restaurant.
        What if we just want to eat some specific dish?
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="col-lg-6">
      <h4>Provide menu information for restaurants</h4>
      <p>
        Provide menu information for restaurants.
        Scalable if we push more review/menu information.
      </p>

    </div>
  </div>

